{"tid":1257752,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【動漫】簡中漫畫、手辦預警！萬代與集英社成立上海合資公司！","createTime":"2019-06-25T17:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T13:31:41.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3b180f20ab82541089ef56284e97959161a0f909","tid":1257752,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"【動漫】簡中漫畫、手辦預警！萬代與集英社成立上海合資公司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gANMoDU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgANMoDU.png&h=dbf21153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  來自日媒今日（6月25日）的最新報導，萬代南夢宮和集英社已經達成合作協議，二者將合資成立集英萬夢(上海)商貿有限公司（集英萬夢（上海）商貿有限公司）。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉，該公司資本金約3億日元，其中萬代投資比例為51％，集英社投資比例為49％。公司計劃於今年10月正式成立，主要負責在中國開展集英社漫畫原作的商品化、企劃、製作、販售等。<br />\n<br />\n  眾所周知，集英社旗下最為知名的就是《周刊少年Jump》雜誌，其漫畫代表作品有《火影忍者》、《海賊王》、《銀魂》、《龍珠》、《JOJO的奇妙冒險》、《遊戲王》、《聖鬥士》、《灌籃高手》、《櫻桃小丸子》等。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jRUxxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jRUxxO.jpg&h=5499021a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18c49cf330d9a24b5cbb8f1546c51482ead6b98c","tid":1257752,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"不反了不反了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQ2Ag0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQ2Ag0v.jpg&h=6d5cb7cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4de0fff5c8851fd4f534852a53cf7aaca05cd43b","tid":1257752,"uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"據悉，該公司資本金約3億日元<br />\n<br />\n得2千萬人仔，用黎請d地方官飲酒疏通都唔夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c41f5c862654d07acc413abdf9182f0385d476","tid":1257752,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"有無比人搶註？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01592e2e096c12410a4f7f3521b194aa5e102ae6","tid